    list_feature_classes(feature_dataset, feature_class)

    list_feature_classes.Rd

    list the feature classes available in ElmerGeo

    Usage

    list_feature_classes(feature_dataset = NULL, feature_class = NULL)

    Arguments

    feature_dataset

    String. If supplied, this filters the list to just those feature classes in the feature dataset

    feature_class

    String. If supplied, this filters the list to just the named one. This can be useful if you know the name of the feature class but not the geography type or the feature dataset that it resides in.

    Value

    A dataframe listing the layer names along with the corresponding feature datasets and geometry types.. Defaults to NULL.

    Examples
